--- Runtime filter ---
Output: a, b, c, x, y

Join (JOIN FillRightFirst)
│  t1 ⋈ t2
│  Type: inner | Strictness: all | Algorithm: ConcurrentHashJoin
│  Join conditions: a = x
│  Output:
│    Left:  a, b, c
│    Right: x, y
├──ReadFromMergeTree (default.t1)
│     Read type: Default
│     Parts: 1 | Granules: 1
│     Output: a, b, c
│     Runtime filters: RF1(a, x from default.t2)
└──BuildRuntimeFilter (Build runtime join filter on x)
   │  Filter id: RF1
   │  Source table: default.t2
   └──ReadFromMergeTree (default.t2)
         Read type: Default
         Parts: 1 | Granules: 1
         Output: x, y
